      <p class="eyebrow">About Roze Health</p>

      <h2>
        A physician-led clinic built around trust, safety, and natural results.
      </h2>

      <p class="lead centered">
        Roze Health was created to offer a more thoughtful medical aesthetics
        experience: one where clinical judgment, patient education, and subtle
        aesthetic outcomes are placed at the centre of care.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-intro reveal">
      <p>
        Our approach is conservative, individualized, and medically grounded.
        Every treatment begins with a detailed consultation, a careful review of
        goals and medical history, and an honest discussion about what treatment
        can and cannot achieve. We believe the best results should look refined,
        balanced, and authentically you.
      </p>
    </div>

